SUMMARY:Collegeville/Perkiomen Trail
DESCRIPTION:Walking Tails\nParking: Don't park in the TD Bank parking lot.
  Instead\, park between the TD Bank and the LabCorp building.\n\nCLICK DIR
 ECTLY ON THE MAP IF YOU THINK YOU ARE LOST. IT WILL BRING YOU RIGHT TO US 
 WHERE WE MEET.\n\nWe will meet in the parking lot then head south on the P
 erkiomen Trail for 1.5 to 2 miles turning around to head back the way we c
 ame when the group wishes\, for a total of 3 to 4 miles. The trail is abou
 t 10-12 feet wide and graveled with tree cover providing shade.\n\nStart T
 ime: We will start hiking promptly at the scheduled time.\n\nDuration of t
 he walk – depends on the people and dogs in the group. We frequently end
  up walking in smaller packs based on the comfort level of the participant
 s.\n\nPlease remember pooh bags and that your dog must be on a leash. Stur
 dy shoes or hiking boots are recommended. Dress appropriately for weather 
 conditions.\n\nNOTICE: By attending this event you are agreeing that YOU A
 RE RESPONSIBLE FOR YOUR OWN SAFETY AT ALL TIMES. The hike leader and other
  members cannot be held responsible for any damages\, accidents\, or liabi
 lities incurred while hiking with us.
